值班人员称，已经登记相关情况，将督促查实。如果属实，相关部门将按照党纪党规处理。 顶端新闻记者注意到，6 月 7 日上午，寰球工程项目管理 (北京) 有限公司的认证微信公众号「北京项目管理公司寰球项目公司」中，关于胡继勇的活动报道被删除。12 时许，该账号被自助注销、停止使用。 天眼查显示，寰球工程项目管理 (北京) 有限公司大股东为中国石油集团工程有限公司 (100% 持股)，成立于 1995 年，位于北京市，是一家以从事专业技术服务业为主的企业。企业注册资本 3000 万人民币，实缴资本 3000 万人民币。国企领导出差带「小三」逛街？中央巡视组回应：将督促查实"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-df4908d4f2a366dbbe96278341820115_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/605268126"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIufH/se2s3thNEAMaCDk2Nzg0MDU2ILHOgKQGMAA4+BhAEHIIOTY3ODQwNTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1686197381.198171", "card_id": "Q_603123126", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 56}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "律师们收到判决书会先看什么部分？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "很好奇，如果律师收到了判决书后，会第一时间看判决结果，还是从头至尾看一遍最后看判决结果呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/603123126"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IufH/se2s3thNEAMaCDk2MzA3NzYxIITOwKMGMAA4OkARcgg5NjMwNzc2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1686197381.198546", "card_id": "Q_604778370", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "由于